title: No Pain - No quit in me.
description:
Ahh after a few hours of mentally exhausting the weather issue, I come to the same conclusion as pre London 2018, There's not an ounce of quit in my body.

Maybe Houston 2019, is a test for Doha 2019, and Tokyo 2020 when weather will be far from perfect.
